<num value="48">辛亥</num>
<pc>，</pc>幸<placeName>玉津園</placeName>宴射<pc>。</pc>京兆府貢野蠶繭<pc>。</pc>
<num value="49">壬子</num>
<pc>，</pc>
<placeName>衡州</placeName>火<pc>。</pc>
<num value="52">乙卯</num>
<pc>，</pc>錄囚<pc>。</pc>
<num value="53">丙辰</num>
<pc>，</pc>河決<placeName>滑州</placeName>
<pc>，</pc>壞靈河大堤<pc>。</pc>普州兔食稼<pc>。</pc>
