</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>　　<measure quantity="9" unit="months">
<num value="9">九</num>月</measure>
<num value="29">壬辰</num>朔<pc>，</pc>水<pc>。</pc>虎捷指揮使孫進<pc>、</pc>龍衛指揮使吳瓌等<measure quantity="27" unit="people">
